longBusinessSummary: Vardhman Acrylics Limited manufactures and supplies acrylic fibers and tows in India. It offers its products under the Varlan brand name. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Ludhiana, India. Vardhman Acrylics Limited operates as a subsidiary of Vardhman Textiles Limited.
